						               													<description>General info on Krimi Total: Murder mystery game in which players act out their role and try to solve the mystery.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Info on this particular case: Blue skies, clear waters, endless white beaches frame the beatiful island republic of Bananas Grandes. For three dacades El Presidente Emilio Mentirosa has governed this trobical island. He likes to be celebrated by the powerful, beatiful and rich. Tonight the champaign is on ice, latin rhythms come from the speakers on the sundeck of the presidential yacht. Tonight El Presidente ce&amp;ouml;ebrates his 60th birthday. As the party is about to begin a body is found on board. Is El Presidentes life in danger? Or maybe even the future of Bananas Grandes?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Die Yacht der Macht there are 8 obligatory roles (can't be played with less than 8): 4 male, 4 female. One optional role, the inspector, can be either male or female. The roles include: El Presidente, his wife and son, the son's girlfriend, the presidents couselor, the general, a rich heiress to the banana plantations and an american buesinessman, looking to bring tourism to Banans Grandes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
